                     <interp inst="t17330510-33-person286" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , which was preferr'd to the Lord Chancellor for superseding the Commission, and was<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="173305100023"></xptr> sign'd by Lordship's his Secretary and Clerk, was produc'd in Court: But there being no legal Proof that it was presented by 
               <persName id="t17330510-33-person287">
                  John 
                  Ford 
               <interp inst="t17330510-33-person287" type="surname" value="Ford"></interp>
